@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@admin = course-alex-local-token

### Start the production-like stack first:
### SOURCE_COMMIT=$(git rev-parse HEAD) SOURCE_BRANCH=$(git branch --show-current) \
### BUILD_TIME=$(date -u +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ) \
### docker compose -f compose.release.yml up --build

### Public deployment identity and provider posture
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/health

### Independent readiness for build, stores, work state, and optional generation
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/operations/readiness

### Seed application-owned source rows
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/seed

### Start the durable backfill
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/migrations/knowledge-articles
Authorization: Bearer {{admin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "batchSize": 3,
  "rateLimit": 0,
  "reindexExisting": false
}

### Create an explicitly non-LLM conversation persistence probe
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/operations/release-probes
Authorization: Bearer {{admin}}

### Run the deterministic evidence-quality gate
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quality/rag/golden
Authorization: Bearer {{admin}}

### Restart only the application, then call readiness and the returned probe conversation URL.
### The database, vectors, chat turn, indexing state, and migration state must remain.

### Remove expired operational state without deleting source rows or vector evidence
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/operations/retention/cleanup
Authorization: Bearer {{admin}}

### Source and vector counts remain; eligible sessions/work rows are gone
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/operations/readiness

### Automated exact-commit proof
### ./scripts/smoke-release.sh
### jq . target/course-release-evidence/release-keyless-summary.json

### Optional hosted-provider proof; writes NOT_RUN when OPENAI_API_KEY is absent
### ./scripts/smoke-openai-optional.sh
### jq . target/course-release-evidence/openai-keyed-summary.json
